Deux!

313
00:20:05.060 --> 00:20:06.270
Collier!
Krah!

314
00:20:11.830 --> 00:20:15.850
Jarret! Collier! Quasi!
Flanchet! Gigot! Selle!

315
00:20:11.830 --> 00:20:15.030
Un! Deux! Ora!

316
